text: Cassipourea swaziensis (Swazi onionwood, ) is a species of plant in the Rhizophoraceae family. It is found in South Africa and Swaziland. It is threatened by habitat loss, and a protected tree in South Africa. ==References== swaziensis Category:Data deficient plants Category:Protected trees of South Africa Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
